statements: SELECT * FROM healthcare_equity;
SELECT patient_name, patient_age FROM healthcare_equity WHERE patient_gender = 'Female';
SELECT patient_id, patient_name, patient_age FROM healthcare_equity ORDER BY patient_age DESC;
SELECT patient_id, patient_name, inclusion_program_name FROM healthcare_equity WHERE inclusion_start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT patient_gender, COUNT(*) AS total_count FROM healthcare_equity GROUP BY patient_gender;
SELECT * FROM healthcare_equity WHERE patient_gender = 'Male';
SELECT patient_name, patient_age, inclusion_program_name FROM healthcare_equity WHERE patient_age > 30;
SELECT patient_name, patient_age, inclusion_program_description FROM healthcare_equity WHERE inclusion_program_id = 'abcdefg';
SELECT patient_id, patient_name, patient_age, inclusion_start_date, inclusion_end_date FROM healthcare_equity WHERE patient_gender = 'Female' AND inclusion_start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM healthcare_equity WHERE patient_age BETWEEN 20 AND 40 ORDER BY patient_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM Diversity_Programs;
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM Diversity_Programs ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT program_name, impact_on_outcomes FROM Diversity_Programs WHERE impact_on_outcomes LIKE '%positive%';
SELECT * FROM Patient_Outcomes WHERE diagnosis = 'cancer';
SELECT patient_id, outcome FROM Patient_Outcomes ORDER BY patient_id ASC;
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM Diversity_Programs;
SELECT * FROM Patient_Outcomes WHERE diagnosis = 'Heart Disease';
SELECT diversity_program_id, program_name, start_date, end_date, impact_on_outcomes FROM Diversity_Programs ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT patient_name, treatment, outcome FROM Patient_Outcomes WHERE outcome = 'Improved' ORDER BY patient_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Diversity_Programs JOIN Patient_Outcomes ON diversity_program_id = patient_id;
SELECT * FROM patients;
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM patients WHERE age > 30;
SELECT patient_name, health_condition FROM patients WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT * FROM diversity_programs ORDER BY program_start_date DESC;
SELECT program_name, program_description FROM diversity_programs WHERE program_start_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT * FROM patients WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT patient_name, age FROM patients ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT patient_name, health_condition FROM patients WHERE age > 30 AND ethnicity = 'Hispanic';
SELECT * FROM diversity_programs WHERE program_start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';

SELECT patients.patient_name, diversity_programs.program_name, patient_outcomes.outcome_description FROM patients JOIN patient_outcomes ON patients.patient_id = patient_outcomes.patient_id JOIN diversity_programs ON patient_outcomes.program_id = diversity_programs.program_id;
SELECT * FROM patients ORDER BY patient_name DESC;
SELECT patient_name, patient_age, patient_gender FROM patients WHERE patient_gender='Female';
SELECT patient_name, patient_age FROM patients WHERE patient_age > 50 ORDER BY patient_age ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT patient_ethnicity FROM patients;
SELECT patient_name, patient_age, patient_gender FROM patients WHERE patient_ethnicity='Hispanic' ORDER BY patient_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM patients WHERE patient_gender = 'Male';
SELECT patient_name, patient_age FROM patients WHERE patient_ethnicity = 'Hispanic' ORDER BY patient_age DESC;
SELECT * FROM patient_outcomes WHERE outcome_type = 'Recovery' AND outcome_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT patient_name, patient_age, patient_gender FROM patients WHERE patient_age > 30 AND patient_ethnicity = 'Black' ORDER BY patient_name;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_outcomes, outcome_type FROM patient_outcomes GROUP BY outcome_type ORDER BY total_outcomes DESC;
SELECT * FROM patients ORDER BY patient_id DESC;
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM patients WHERE age > 30 AND race = 'Asian';
SELECT patient_id, patient_name, ethnicity FROM patients WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT * FROM diversity_programs ORDER BY start_date ASC, end_date DESC;
SELECT program_name, program_description FROM diversity_programs WHERE end_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM patients;
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM patients WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY gender DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT race, ethnicity FROM patients WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT program_name, program_description, start_date, end_date FROM diversity_programs WHERE end_date > '2022-01-01';

SELECT pr.outcome, pr.outcome_date, pp.participant_name, pp.participant_role FROM patient_records pr JOIN program_participants pp ON pr.patient_id = pp.patient_id AND pr.program_id = pp.program_id ORDER BY pr.outcome_date DESC, pp.participant_name ASC;
